import { View, ImageBackground, Image, StyleSheet, Scrol } from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'
import Text from '../../components/Text'
import images from '../../assets/image/'
import { HEIGHT, WIDTH } from '../../assets/styles'

export default function Profile() {
    return (
    <ScrollView contentContainerStyle={styles.container}>
    <ImageBackground
    source={images.BG_PROFILE}
    resizeMode='cover'
    style={styles.background}
    >
    <View style={styles.imageContainer}>
    <Image
    source={images.PERSON2}
    style={styles.person}
    />
    </View>
    <Text fontSize={20} bold style={styles.name}>Ahmad Akbar Maulana</Text>
    <Text color="#909090" style={styles.role}>React Native Developer</Text>
    <View style={styles.infoContainer}>
    <View style={styles.rowContainer}>
    <Text style={styles.label}>ID</Text>
    <Text color="#A7A7A7" style={styles.value}>A20134</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.divider} />
    <View style={styles.rowContainer}>
    <Text style={styles.label}>Email</Text>
    <Text color="#A7A7A7" style={styles.value}>siapayaamanyanyah@gmail.com</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.divider} />
    <View style={styles.rowContainer}>
    <Text style={styles.label}>Date of Birth</Text>
    <Text color="#A7A7A7" style={styles.value}>3 May 1999</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.divider} />
    <View style={styles.rowContainer}>
    <Text style={styles.label}>Gender</Text>
    <Text color="#A7A7A7" style={styles.value}>Male</Text>
    </View>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.teamContainer}>
    <Text bold style={styles.teamText}>Team</Text>
    <Text color="#A7A7A7" style={styles.teamName}>React Native</Text>
    <View style={styles.teamMembers}>
    <Image source={images.PERSON3} style={styles.otherPerson} />
    <Image source={images.PERSON4} style={styles.otherPerson} />
    <Image source={images.PERSON5} style={styles.otherPerson} />
    <Image source={images.ELIPSE} style={styles.otherPerson} />
    <Text color="#FFFF" style={styles.othersPerson}>+6</Text>
    </View>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.settingsContainer}>
    <View style={styles.settingItem}>
    <Image source={images.GUARD} style={styles.settingIcon} />
    <Text style={styles.settingLabel}>Privacy And Security</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.settingDivider} />
    <View style={styles.settingItem}>
    <Image source={images.HELP} style={styles.settingIcon} />
    <Text style={styles.settingLabel}>Help</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.settingDivider} />
    <View style={styles.settingItem}>
    <Image source={images.ABOUT} style={styles.settingIcon} />
    <Text style={styles.settingLabel}>About Us</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.settingDivider} />
    <View style={styles.settingItem}>
    <Image source={images.LOGOUT} style={styles.settingIcon} />
    <Text style={styles.settingLabel}>Logout</Text>
    </View>
    <Text fontSize={14} bold style={styles.versionText}>v.0.0.1</Text>
    </View>
    <View style={styles.bottomNav}>
    <Image source={images.HOME} style={styles.bottomNavItem} />
    <Image source={images.TASK} style={styles.bottomNavItem} />
    <Image source={images.BG} style={styles.bottomNavItem} />
    <Image source={images.PERFORM} style={styles.bottomNavItem} />
    <Image source={images.PROFILE} style={styles.bottomNavItem} />
    </View>
    <View style={styles.bottomNavLabels}>
    <Text color="#CED1D4" fontSize={10}>Home</Text>
    <Text color="#CED1D4" fontSize={10}>Task</Text>
    <Text color="#CED1D4" fontSize={10}>Performance</Text>
    <Text color='#04325F' bold fontSize={10}>Profile</Text>
    </View>
    </ImageBackground>
    </ScrollView>
    );
    }

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    background: {
        width: WIDTH,
        height: 495,
        paddingTop: 90,
        alignItems: 'center',
    },
    person: {
        width: 120,
        height: 120,
        borderRadius: 90,
    },
    otherPerson: {
        width: 35,
        height: 35,
        borderRadius: 90,
        marginLeft: 'auto',
        border: 1,
        borderColor: "#FFF",
        marginRight: 16,
        marginTop: 17,
        marginBottom: 17,
    },
    othersPerson: {
        marginLeft: -43,
        marginRight: 25,
        marginTop: 25,
        marginBottom: 26,
    },
    rectang: {
        paddingHorizontal: 16,
        backgroundColor: "#fff",
        borderRadius: 12,
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.3,
        shadowRadius: 4,
        elevation: 5,
        marginHorizontal: 20,
        paddingBottom: 16
    },
    rowContainer: {
        justifyContent: "space-between",
        padding: 5,
        flexDirection: "row",
    },
    label: {
        fontSize: 14,
        fontWeight: 'bold',
        paddingTop: 16,
    },
    label1: {
        fontSize: 14,
        fontWeight: 'bold',
        marginTop: 16,
        alignSelf: 'center',
    },

    value: {
        fontSize: 14,
        color: "#A7A7A7",
        paddingTop: 16,
        paddingLeft: 16,
    },
    divider: {
        paddingTop: 13,
        paddingLeft: 16,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
    },
    dividerLine: {
        paddingHorizontal: 16,
        height: 1,
        width: 311.00644,
        borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3',
        borderBottomWidth: 1,
    },
    rectang2: {
        marginTop: 20,
        width: 343,
        height: 70,
        paddingHorizontal: 16,
        backgroundColor: "#fff",
        borderRadius: 12,
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.3,
        shadowRadius: 4,
        elevation: 5,
    },
    rectang3: {
        alignSelf: "center",
        marginVertical: 20,
        width: 343,
        height: 186,
        paddingHorizontal: 16,
        backgroundColor: "#fff",
        borderRadius: 12,
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.3,
        shadowRadius: 4,
        elevation: 5,
        marginBottom: 20
    },
    btnDown: {
        width: 24,
        height: 24,
        borderRadius: 90,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderColor: "#FFF",
        marginTop: 14,
        marginRight: 11
    }
});
